**********************************************************************
MAUI hello demo code
**********************************************************************
What this demo does:
  - "Hello MAUI demo..." is displayed. The message is displayed for 10
    seconds and then the demo terminates.
 
**********************************************************************
System requirements:
  - A working MAUI environment is assumed.
  - The demo requires that gfx is in memory.
  - The demo requires that mfm is in memory.
 
*********************************************************************
Directories: 
  - Source code 
      $MWOS/SRC/MAUI/DEMOS/HELLO

  - Assets
      $MWOS/<operating system>/<hardware platform>/ASSETS/FONTS
        
*********************************************************************
To make this demo:
  - From the source file directory type:
      % os9make
 
*********************************************************************
Operation:

  - If no command line options are used, the font 'default.fnt' must
    be in memory. The font can be found in the assets directory noted
    above.

      $ hello

  - Alternatively, the -f option can be used to specify an alternative
    font.

      $ hello -f=myfont.ucm

*********************************************************************

